data.description: Charming 1 bedroom, 1 bath condo in "Casa La Paz". Just 144 units right across the street from shopping and restaurants. This is a single level, upstairs end unit with balcony. Amenities include pool, spa, clubhouse and adjacent huge private park with picnic tables, two lighted tennis courts, a fenced dog park and ball fields, all for exclusive use of residents. This perfect location is just a few minutes to the 73-toll road and the 5 Fwy, and about 15–20-minute drive to beautiful Laguna Beach and Dana Point. Stainless appliances and microwave, wood flooring & new carpeting in the bedroom which features a walk-in closet. Added ceiling fan in eating area for great air circulation. Inside stacking washer/dryer closet for convenience, Washer/dryer and refrigerator stays.  HOA.
